Task
Number of pairs of positive elements
Write a function counOfPositivePairs that takes an array arr as an argument and returns the number of pairs of adjacent elements that are positive numbers.
Example:
• the function counOfPositivePairs ([0, 25, 3, -2, 5]) must return 1 (there is only one such pair: 25 and 3)
• the function counOfPositivePairs ([2, -2, 5]) must return 0.
• the counOfPositivePairs ([]) function must return 0.

Solution
function counOfPositivePairs (arr) {
 let pairs = 0;
 for (let i = 0; i <arr.length; i ++) {
  if (arr [i]> 0 && arr [i + 1]> 0)
  pairs ++;
  }
  return pairs;
}
